  <div id="text-content_9968fb29-dc32-41ea-8f9b-f0518fc2f1d6" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you create a new quiz through an assignment group and do not add quiz questions, the quiz will be worth zero points in the Gradebook. You need to add questions to the quiz before students take the quiz in Canvas. To display points possible for the quiz, add quiz questions to the quiz. Otherwise, you can change the assignment type to something else, such as No Submission or On Paper.</p>
