      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_6e1ea289-48ba-4072-a57a-81cbdfb90ad4" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If a quiz is taken in a classroom or outside of Canvas, you should create an assignment using the No Submission submission type. This assignment type allows you to manually set the points possible and enter grades for your students. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

